The paper discusses the combination of two frameworks, one for reasoning about concurrent programs and the other for reasoning about weighted programs. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper introduces a family of logics, which may fall under the Programming Languages (cs.PL) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the validity of axioms, which may relate to Software Engineering (cs.SE) or Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
